{"TopicId":207704,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Kerbal Contract. Test the AE-FF1 Airstream Protective Shell","CreatedByName":"Jamesg5000","CreatedById":220934,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-12T00:17:52Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Jamesg5000","CreatedById":220934,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-12T00:17:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am stuck on this contact. Requirements are\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. Orbit\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. The sun\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI get the checkmark when I orbit Kerbin. What do I need to do for the Sun?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Snark","CreatedById":125662,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-12T00:26:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224115346\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207704\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221649722672\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022220934\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jamesg5000\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, Jamesg5000 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am stuck on this contact. Requirements are\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. Orbit\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. The sun\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI get the checkmark when I orbit Kerbin. What do I need to do for the Sun?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello, and welcome to the forums! \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat those requirements mean is that you need to be in orbit around the Sun (not orbit of Kerbin).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey\u0027re listed that way because it\u0027s two separate requirements, and you need to satisfy both of them simultaneously. You need to be in orbit, and the thing you are orbiting needs to be the sun.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo be in orbit of the sun, that means you need to escape Kerbin\u0027s \u0022sphere of influence\u0022 (typically abbreviated \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Sphere of Influence\u0022\u003ESoI\u003C/abbr\u003E). In Kerbin\u0027s case, it has a radius of roughly 84,000 km, or not quite twice the distance of Minmus.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo,all you need to do is boost your craft until it escapes Kerbin\u0027s sphere of influence, and there you go.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jamesg5000","CreatedById":220934,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-12T00:47:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks! Ill give that a try\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fleventeen","CreatedById":220622,"CreatedDateTime":"2022-04-12T04:59:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224115360\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022207704\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221649724461\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022220934\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jamesg5000\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Jamesg5000 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks! Ill give that a try\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRemember that your return to Kerbin will be at (a minimum) escape velocity, so don\u0027t forget the heatshield! It can get a little toasty out there.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGL!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}